channel.title: Should I worry that interface does not always behave the same way?
channel.description:
For example, sometimes the desktop toolbox (square with three horizontal lines) is not displayed, more precisely, a black square is displayed instead.
Another example: position of the WhonixCheck window showing the result of the check is not always the same.
